{1}^{o}(D)$ and $\\gamma(D)$ can be\narbitrary large for directed trees and connected functional digraphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 May 2019 16:26:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
